  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "For instance, the authors in [86] evaluated both traditional machine learning algorithms (such as KNN, random forests RF, decision trees DT, among others) as well as extreme learning machines (ELMs) and Long-Short-Term Memory networks (LSTM) for board game interaction analysis.",
    "The results show that ELMs and LSTM perform best for expressive moment detection whereas random forests perform best for emotional expression classification.Earlier techniques did not consider the temporal information and environmental conditions in emotion recognition.",
    "However, temporal and environmental factors have been deemed increasingly important for emotion recognition as shown by some recent techniques.",
    "For example, the authors in [87] showed the importance of temporal information in emotion detection by proposing a Coupled Hidden Markov Model (CHMM)-based multimodal fusion approach to modeling the contextual information based on the temporal change of facial expressions and speech responses for mood disorder detection.",
    "The speech and facial features were used to construct the SVM-based detector for emotion profile generation."
  ],
